@DATABASE "Virus Info Base"
@NODE MAIN "T.F.C. Revenge V1.03"
     Name         : T.F.C. Revenge V1.03

     Aliases      : No aliases

     Original     : Extreme

     Type/size    : Boot/1024

     Symptoms     : Shows an alert.

     Discovered   : 06-02-92

     Way to infect: Boot infection

     Rating       : Dangerous

     Kickstarts   : 1.2/1.3/2.0

     Damage       : Fastformat of all disks.

     Manifestation: In the boot you can read: "T.F.C. Revenge ...etc"

     Removal      : Install boot

     Comments     : The virus is resident by using the KICK-Vectors.
                    It uses DoIO() to infect other Disks. Additionaly
                    it patches $90(a6)-Interrupt. This patch sets the
                    KICK-Vectors always to the virus-value. After 3
                    infects a fastformat-routine will be started (all
                    disks BAD!) and an alert will shown:

                    The Fanatic Crew

                                  proudly presents

                            T.F.C. Revenge V1.03 Virus...etc

                    Click on this gadget to see a  @{" Demo " SYSTEM V-IFF:TFCRevenge} of the TFC 
                    Revenge virus. Push left mouse button to return.



                    After presing any mouse button the AMIGA resets.
                    This Virus is a clone of the Extreme "Antivirus".

A.D 12-93
@ENDNODE
